title: Over the Calf Work Socks for Men and Women 9-11 10-13 13-15 Moisture Wicking Tall Cushioned Knee High Boot Socks 6-pack
description: EVERYDAY COMFORT: Take your over the calf work sock and throw it out, because this is the OTC sock to end all over the calf socks. With features like seamless toe, cushioned foot, stay-put arch band, reinforced toe and heel, and a ribbed leg, you will be wearing the gold standard in comfortable, durable socks.

BREATHABLE DRY TECHNOLOGY: Knit from an ultra soft, spun polyester and featuring mesh panels for extra breathability and sweat wicking, these TCK Over the Calf Socks keep your feet dry and comfortable all season long- making them the best socks for sweaty feet!

PADDED COMFORT: Strategically placed cushioning along the footbed designed to cradle your feet in all day comfort, whether standing on concrete, working construction, wearing cowboy boots, hunting or more.

SUPERIOR FIT: A light compression band around the arch of the foot ensures that our socks stay in place and do not slip or slide. A smooth toe seam keeps your toes happy and not bunched up inside your shoe. They are an over the calf length making them an ideal length for tall boots.

SOCK & SIZING INFORMATION: Medium (Women's Shoe Size: 5-10. Men's Shoe Size 6-9) Large (Women's Shoe Size 10-13. Men's Shoe Size 9-12). X-Large (Men's Shoe Size of 12 - 15). Made of high quality materials. Made of 96% Polyester, 3% Rubber, 1% Spandex.
